This is a just a quick reminder to myself about a cpanel git issue that I&rsquo;ve found a fix for.
When accessing a git remote from a webphosting provider thru ssh, you may get the error&hellip; &ldquo;fatal: bad config value for &lsquo;receive.denycurrentbranch&rsquo; in ./config&rdquo;
The fix for it was simple after you realize what&rsquo;s going on. It turns out that there are sometimes more than one version of git installed in web-hosting providers.

